INSERT INTO aggregator.user_history_limit
                SELECT
                    market_id,
                    order_id,
                    user,
                    custodian_id,
                    side,
                    self_match_behavior,
                    restriction,
                    price,
                    (txn_version * POWER(2,64::numeric) + event_idx)
                FROM place_limit_order_events
                WHERE txn_version > $1
